<area shape="rect" id="node9" title="dsgrid.config.mapping_tables.MappingTableByNameModel

Attributes for a dimension mapping table for soon&#45;to&#45;be registered dimensions by name.
This will be converted to a MappingTableModel as soon as the dimensions are registered.

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;mapping_type (DimensionMappingType(DSGEnum)): Type/purpose of the dimension mapping. Default is &#39;many_to_one_aggregation&#39;.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;archetype (Optional[DimensionMappingArchetype(DSGEnum)]): Dimension mapping archetype, determined based on mapping_type. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;description (str): Description of dimension mapping
 &#160;&#160;&#160;from_fraction_tolerance (Optional[float]): Tolerance value to apply to the from_fraction column. Default is 1e&#45;09.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;to_fraction_tolerance (Optional[float]): Tolerance value to apply to the to_fraction column. Default is 1e&#45;09.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;filename (str): Filename containing association table records.
" alt="" coords="2873,3755,3607,3951"/>
<area shape="rect" id="node10" title="dsgrid.config.project_config.DimensionsModel

Contains dimensions defined by a project

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;base_dimensions (List[Union[DimensionModel, DateTimeDimensionModel, AnnualTimeDimensionModel, RepresentativePeriodTimeDimensionModel, NoOpTimeDimensionModel]]): List of dimensions for a project&#39;s base dimensions. They will be automatically registered during project registration and then converted to base_dimension_references. Default is [].
 &#160;&#160;&#160;base_dimension_references (List[DimensionReferenceModel]): List of registry references (``DimensionReferenceModel``) for a project&#39;s base dimensions. Default is [].
 &#160;&#160;&#160;subset_dimensions (list[SubsetDimensionGroupModel]): List of subset dimension groups. Default is [].
 &#160;&#160;&#160;supplemental_dimensions (List[SupplementalDimensionModel]): List of supplemental dimensions. They will be automatically registered during project registration and then converted to supplemental_dimension_references. Default is [].
 &#160;&#160;&#160;supplemental_dimension_references (List[DimensionReferenceModel]): List of registry references for a project&#39;s supplemental dimensions. Default is [].
" alt="" coords="5,2270,1897,2438"/>
<area shape="rect" id="node11" title="dsgrid.config.project_config.SubsetDimensionGroupModel

Defines one or more subset dimension selectors for a dimension type.

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;dimension_query_name (Optional[str]): Auto&#45;generated query name for SQL queries. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;dimension_type (DimensionType(DSGEnum)): Type of the dimension
 &#160;&#160;&#160;filename (Optional[str]): Filename containing dimension records. Only populated for initial registration. Each selector&#39;s records are stored as JSON objects in the dsgrid registry. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;selectors (list[SubsetDimensionSelectorModel]): Dimension selectors
 &#160;&#160;&#160;selector_references (list[DimensionReferenceModel]): References to the subset dimensions generated by dsgrid during registration. Default is [].
 &#160;&#160;&#160;create_supplemental_dimension (bool): Auto&#45;generate supplemental dimensions in order to allow aggregrations on the subsets. Default is True.
" alt="" coords="2050,2921,2721,3229"/>
